original_title: Paw Patrol:  Pups Save the Bunnies
overview: Help the PAW Patrol on a bunny rabbit rescue, and then hop into 6 other springtime tales, including a double-length mission to save Adventure Bay's Easter Egg Hunt!  Plus, protect Farmer Yumi's vegetable garden, Mayor Goodway's tulips, missing songbirds and MORE!
title: Paw Patrol:  Pups Save the Bunnies
